Description:
    Creates a new front-end web application based on Bourbon Neat (lightweight, semantic Sass grid).

Options:
    Normalize: Include Normalize-css (alternative reset)
    Modernizer: Include Modernizer.js

Example:
    yo bourbon-neat

    This will create:
        Gruntfile.js: Configuration for the task runner.
        bower.json: Front-end packages installed by bower.
        package.json: Development packages installed by npm.

        app/: Your application files.
        test/: Unit tests for your application.
